{"data":[{"name":"82:1","price":"1. Quand le ciel se brisera,","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ ٱنفَطَرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5830,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:2","price":"2. quand les astres choiront,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡكَوَاكِبُ ٱنتَثَرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5831,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:3","price":"3. que les mers se confondront,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡبِحَارُ فُجِّرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5832,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:4","price":"4. que les tombes seront renversées,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡقُبُورُ بُعۡثِرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5833,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:5","price":"5. chaque âme saura alors ce qu’elle a déjà fait et ce qu’elle a renvoyé à plus tard.","arabic":"عَلِمَتۡ نَفۡسٞ مَّا قَدَّمَتۡ وَأَخَّرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5834,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:6","price":"6. Ô homme ! Qu’est-ce qui t’a donc leurré au sujet de ton Noble Seigneur","arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَا غَرَّكَ بِرَبِّكَ ٱلۡكَرِيمِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5835,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:7","price":"7. Qui t’a créé, t’a façonné et t’a donné des formes aussi proportionnées ?","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَكَ فَسَوَّىٰكَ فَعَدَلَكَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5836,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:8","price":"8. Il t’a constitué dans la forme qu’Il a voulue.","arabic":"فِيٓ أَيِّ صُورَةٖ مَّا شَآءَ رَكَّبَكَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5837,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:9","price":"9. Et pourtant, vous tenez la Rétribution pour imposture.","arabic":"كَلَّا بَلۡ تُكَذِّبُونَ بِٱلدِّينِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5838,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:10","price":"10. Des gardiens sont là à vous surveiller,","arabic":"وَإِنَّ عَلَيۡكُمۡ لَحَٰفِظِينَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5839,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:11","price":"11. qui sont de nobles scripteurs,[597]","arabic":"كِرَامٗا كَٰتِبِينَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5840,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[597] Sur le choix de ce mot, au lieu de « scribe » ou « écrivain », voir la note 105. ","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:12","price":"12. sachant bien ce que vous faites.","arabic":"يَعۡلَمُونَ مَا تَفۡعَلُونَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5841,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:13","price":"13. Les vertueux auront droit au délice absolu.","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡأَبۡرَارَ لَفِي نَعِيمٖ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5842,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:14","price":"14. Les scélérats seront en Enfer.","arabic":"وَإِنَّ ٱلۡفُجَّارَ لَفِي جَحِيمٖ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5843,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:15","price":"15. Ils y brûleront au Jour de la Rétribution,","arabic":"يَصۡلَوۡنَهَا يَوۡمَ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5844,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:16","price":"16. et ne pourront s’y dérober.","arabic":"وَمَا هُمۡ عَنۡهَا بِغَآئِبِينَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5845,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:17","price":"17. Et qui te fera jamais savoir ce qu’est le Jour de la Rétribution ?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا يَوۡمُ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5846,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:18","price":"18. Et puis, qui te fera jamais savoir ce qu’est le Jour de la Rétribution ?","arabic":"ثُمَّ مَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا يَوۡمُ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5847,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"82:19","price":"19. C’est le jour où aucune âme ne pourra rien pour une autre âme. Et la décision, ce jour-là, reviendra entière à Allah.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ لَا تَمۡلِكُ نَفۡسٞ لِّنَفۡسٖ شَيۡـٔٗاۖ وَٱلۡأَمۡرُ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلَّهِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5848,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"}],"chapter":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar","Chapter Al-Infitar","Infitar","Surah Infitar","Chapter Infitar","Al Infitar","Surah Al Infitar","Chapter Al Infitar","Surah 82","Chapter 82","The Cleaving","الإنفطار"]}